            <title>香港搶先睇 Tesla Optimus 機械人　同場展出 Cybertruck、Model 3 + Model Y 新閃電銀色</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/tesla-optimus-robot-in-element/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-optimus-robot-in-element</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/tesla-optimus-robot-in-element/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:30:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
