            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258624</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 在香港圓方舉辦「遇見未來 Meet The Future」限定體驗活動，今次更是 Tesla 首次在香港展示旗下先進機械人產品—Tesla Optimus。同場亦展出了極具未來感的 Cybertruck 及全新 Quicksilver 閃電銀色車色版本 Model 3 和 Model Y。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Optimus 機械人（又名 Tesla Bot）是一款設計靈感來自人類形態的人形機械人，專為替代人類進行重複、枯燥或危險工作而研發。Optimus 採用與 Tesla 電動車相同人工智能 AI 技術，能夠安全高效地在複雜環境中自主導航及操作人類工具、搬運貨物，以及在工廠裏工作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Optimus</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手部設計可操作人類工具</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可搬運貨物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲具有多個活動關節</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲採用與 Tesla 電動車相同人工智能 AI 技術</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>Cybertruck 是一輛外觀設計具有未來感，同時兼顧實用性和跑車性能的電動卡車，擁有卓越的耐用性及全地形駕駛能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258707" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Tesla 同場展示了全新 Quicksilver 閃電銀色 Model 3 和 Model Y，這款顏色會隨光線及觀看角度變化呈現不同視覺效果，令車身流線設計更加突出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 閃電銀色 Model Y</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 閃電銀色 Model Y</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 閃電銀色 Model 3</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 閃電銀色 Model 3</p><p>Tesla 同時推出針對 Model 3 和 Model Y 後輪驅動版本的免息分期貸款計劃，名額有限，先到先得。有興趣試駕的朋友可透過 Tesla 官方網站 <a href="https://bit.ly/TeslaMeetTheFuture">https://bit.ly/TeslaMeetTheFuture</a> 預約，或致電 3975-0254 查詢詳情。</p><h2>「遇見未來 Meet The Future」限定體驗活動</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>日期：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">2024 年 8 月 24 日至 9 月 1 日</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>時間：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">11:00-20:00</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>地點：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">圓方金區 1 樓</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/23/tesla-drive-anywhere-package-us/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 美國推出新服務計劃，超級充電站 FSD 自動駕駛 3 年任用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/eu-update-chinese-ev-tariffs/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">歐盟調低中國電動車額外關税，三大中國車企減幅極少 Tesla 受惠最大</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/13/donald-trump-elon-musk-talk-on-x/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">特朗普馬斯克網絡對談聽眾過百萬　讚揚 Tesla 電動車「不可思議」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/tesla-optimus-robot-in-element/life-tech/auto/">香港搶先睇 Tesla Optimus 機械人　同場展出 Cybertruck、Model 3 + Model Y 新閃電銀色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
